    "title": "Manufacturing Engineer - Birla Tyres Holdings Services - Growth Opportunity",
    "description": "Birla Tyres Holdings Services has an exciting opening for a Manufacturing Engineer at our Indore office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Birla Tyres Holdings Services:\nBirla Tyres Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in FMEA\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in Quality Control\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Indore, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Birla Tyres Holdings Services!",
